=== SIGNATURE ===
rev(arr)
=== COMMENT ===
Cleans and reverses an array (same as xtocol(arr, 0, , "←↑")).
=== CODE ===
=LAMBDA(arr, xtocol(arr, 0, , arrow("L") & arrow("U")))
=== DESCRIPTION ===
Reverses the order of an array.

Arguments:
  arr - the array to reverse.

Returns:
  The cleaned, fully reversed array (equivalent to xtocol(arr, 0, , "←↑")).

Example:
  rev({1;2;3})  ->  {3;2;1}
